{"data":[{"date":"07:25 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; khi gi\u1eef l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +5 (b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt song t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1ea3ng D do h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 fair-play. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec sau 90 ph\u00fat, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nhat-Ban-(16h00-ngay-198)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, d\u00f9 th\u1eafng, h\u00f2a hay b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo 99% kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 16 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng nh\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Uzbekistan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh 1 su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng &ldquo;bu\u00f4ng&rdquo; tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u nay nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang D ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng D ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bang-D-ASIAD.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n &ndash; khi danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb U21 tham d\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ecd s\u00e1t v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020, k\u1ef3 th\u1ebf v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng toan t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nhat Ban\" title=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 Thebault Yamaguchi v\u00e0 Tatsuya Ito. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21, song ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eeb c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110TQG. Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 l\u1ea7n so t\u00e0i cao th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mang t\u00ednh danh d\u1ef1.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sau l\u00fac n\u00e0y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, V\u0103n Thanh; \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi; Teruki Hara; Honoya Shoji; Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani; Itsuki Urata; Koji Miyoshi; Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa; Ren Komatsu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 0-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5648","checkdouble":"194784"},{"date":"07:10 19/08","title":"Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Alaves, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Barcelona gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1eadp n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho La Liga.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19, Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Barcelona \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Alaves v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-0. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Barca, Messi c\u00f2n l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000 t\u1ea1i La Liga. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00f2n th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh \"Leo\" ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00f2n 5.000 cho La Liga v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho La Liga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Messi g\u1ed3m Manuel Parera (1 - 1929), Marcos Aurelio (1.000 - 1950), Pedro Tomas Zaballa (2.000 - 1964), Quini (3.000 - 1982), Guillermo Amor (4.000 - 1996).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6.4% trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 6.000 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i La Liga, Lionel Messi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6.4% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 15 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i La Liga trong th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 21.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu-184-194514.html\">Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-boca-juniors-23h15-ngay-158-joan-gamper-372-194556.html\">Barca 3-0 Boca Juniors: C\u00fap Joan Gamper ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5647","checkdouble":"194781"},{"date":"07:48 19/08","title":"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5646","checkdouble":"194785"},{"date":"08:31 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 20/8): Barca g\u1ecdi, Real s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-getafe-3h15-ngay-208-barca-goi-real-se-tra-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Getafe kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu &ndash; tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Th\u1eadt may, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung Getafe.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Nhan-dinh-Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-(3h15-ngay-208)-Barca-goi,-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Getafe</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Real nh\u01b0ng CLB Getafe ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Los Blancos \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o, t\u1eeb b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn danh ti\u1ebfng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Geta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n Real, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Getafe. C\u00f2n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008/09 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Getafe \u0111\u00e3 9 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Getafe, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 khi m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd Lopetegui<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Getafe v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Real. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u00edt \u1ecfi t\u1ea1i Real, vi\u1ec7c Lopetegui c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n La Liga s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui noi cung sau tran thua Atletico Madrid.\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn sau khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8 chung cu\u1ed9c. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Real, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Getafe kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0&nbsp; David Soria, Vitorino Antunes, Ignasi Miquel v\u00e0 Nemanja Maksimovic.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 Cristiano Ronaldo sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Los Blancos v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;con m\u1ed3i ngon&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Real Madrid h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Getafe v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lopetegui \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 La Liga s\u1ebd v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid: \u00c1lvaro Odriozola, Jes\u00fas Vallejo (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe: Markel Bergara (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Djen\u00e9 Dakonam (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid (4-3-3): Navas; Ramos, Varane, Carvajal, Marcelo; Casemiro, Isco, Kroos; Bale, Asensio, Benzema.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe (4-4-2): Soria; Gonzalez, Dakoman, Suarez, Antunes; Maksimovic, Portillo, Ndiaye; Molina, Rodriguez.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n&nbsp;Real Madrid vs Getafe: 2-1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid trong su\u1ed1t 18 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\">S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018</span><br>\r\nSau bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, Atletico Madrid cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Atletico trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5645","checkdouble":"194788"},{"date":"07:17 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield (19h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8): \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c n\u1eefa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League, Manchester City kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi v\u1eabn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng tr\u1ea3i qua ba th\u00e1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hai b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u01a1i x\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Man City c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 n\u00e9t \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng Nicolas Otamendi, David Silva hay c\u1ea3 Kevin De Bruyne, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn b\u0103ng b\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ba th\u00e1ng xem ra kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eb7n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00eanh thang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i mang t\u00ean Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng De Bruyne, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ef5 ng\u00e3, th\u1ebf n\u00ean nh\u1eefng Huddersfield hay Wolverhampton, Newcastle, Fulham, Cardiff, Brighton s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Bernardo Silva nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne, hay t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Riyad Mahrez, c\u1ea3 Benjamin Mendy v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tran Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Sterling tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Du-am-Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-Anh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Etihad c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town c\u00f3 ch\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0ng \u00edt b\u00e0n thua c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i, trong khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3, Huddersfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 David Wagner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/10/DcyGxr0W4AA33Sj.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Huddersfield: H\u00e3y c\u1ee9 tin \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng bao ng\u1edd ng\u1eebng!</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Chelsea ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Stamford Bridge, Huddersfield tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ef1c cho ri\u00eang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ef1a trung l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Etihad g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00ednh Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady n\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 vua ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Man-City-vs-Huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City (4-3-3): 31. Ederson; 2. Walker \u2013 5. Stones \u2013 14. Laporte \u2013 22. Mendy; 8. Gundogan \u2013 25. Fernandinho \u2013 20. Bernardo; 26. Mahrez \u2013 33. Jesus \u2013 7. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huddersfield (4-2-3-1): 12. Hamer; 33. Hadergjonaj \u2013 26. Schindler \u2013 5. Kongolo \u2013 15. Lowe; 10. Mooy \u2013 6. Hogg; 17. Van La Parra \u2013 21. Pritchard \u2013 11. Diakhaby; 24. Mounie<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield: 4-0<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5644","checkdouble":"194783"},{"date":"08:34 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-brighton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 Old Trafford \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manchester United b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i ren \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 xoay quanh Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn t\u1eeb ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Paul Pogba.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" title=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Preview-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City gi\u00fap Man Utd tr\u00fat b\u1ecf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eefng tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, v\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft tinh th\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU khi m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, h\u1ecd cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi phong \u0111\u1ed9, khi Pogba v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo tay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong khi Luke Shaw c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh Pogba l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u1ee1m \u1edd kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mourinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Falmer, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ra ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0o v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n r\u1eddi mi\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 ba t\u00e2n binh Premier League trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u0169ng c\u00e0ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n khi tr\u00f4ng sang t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Brighton g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 thay m\u00e1u to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi chia tay \u0111\u1ebfn 28 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eafn b\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n sau khi h\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho 16 t\u00e2n binh khao kh\u00e1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Watford trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u00e8 v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t qua s\u00e1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brighton ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Cho n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Falmer trong m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch MU t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brighton (4-4-1-1): 1. Ryan; 22. Montoya \u2013 4. Duffy \u2013 5. Dunk \u2013 30. Bernardo; 16. Jahanbakhsh \u2013 6. Stephens \u2013 8. Bissouma \u2013 20. March; 13. Gross \u2013 17. Murray<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd (4-3-3): 1. De Gea; 18. Young \u2013 3. Bailly \u2013 2. Lindelof \u2013 23. Shaw; 17. Fred \u2013 15. Pereira \u2013 6. Pogba; 8. Mata \u2013 9. Lukaku \u2013 7. Sanchez<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU: 1-2<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5643","checkdouble":"194787"},{"date":"03:32 19/08","title":"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Allegri cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A d\u00f9 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Juve v\u00e0 Chievo v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng CR7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Serie A. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Allegri v\u1eabn khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong v\u00f2ng 7 ng\u00e0y qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Sorrentino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Ronaldo h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chievo ch\u1ec9 sau 3 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mattia Bani v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Federico Bernardeschi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\">Chievo 2-3 Juventus: Ronaldo im \u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-juve-chia-tay-marchisio-sau-25-nam-gan-bo-176-194689.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5642","checkdouble":"194772"},{"date":"01:37 19/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Guingamp 1-3 PSG (V\u00f2ng 2 Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/video-tong-hop-guingamp-13-psg-vong-2-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2>\r\nB\u00c0N TH\u1eaeNG<br>\r\nGuingamp: Nolan Roux (20')<br>\r\nPSG: Neymar (pen, 53'), Mbappe (82, 90')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp, HLV Thomas Tuchel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Edinson Cavani hay Mbappe. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, PSG \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, PSG c\u00f2n su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf ph\u00fat 13 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Buffon v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. B\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nolan Roux \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Buffon v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn x\u00e0 ngang. D\u00f9 Roux \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 20, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Colin Dagba c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 Marcus Regis Coco \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m. Coco chuy\u1ec1n cho Roux d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Guingamp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HLV Tuchel bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tung qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u. Ph\u00fat 53, Neymar t\u1ef1 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho PSG. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Guingamp c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ec PSG s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t Mbappe thi\u00ean t\u00e0i. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 2 b\u00e0n cho PSG \u1edf ph\u00fat 82 v\u00e0 90 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tuchel l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau 2 tr\u1eadn, PSG v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u Ligue 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Guingamp \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 18 sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n<br>\r\nGuingamp: Johnsson; Ikoko, Kerbrat, Eboa, Rebocho; Didot (Sorbon 81'), Blas, Coco, Benezet (Rodelin 66'), Thuram (Salibur 75'); Roux<br>\r\nPSG: Buffon; Dagba, Marquinhos, Silva, Meunier; Bernede (Lo Celso 80'), Rabiot, Nkunku (Diaby 74'); Neymar, Di Maria, Weah (Mbappe 46')<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5641","checkdouble":"194767"},{"date":"19:59 18/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8.</h2><h2>Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0 3.4 b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Man United v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Negredo s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Monaco</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;T\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Negredo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Monaco t\u1eeb Besiktas. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Gonalons ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Sevilla</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd La Gazzetta dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Maxime Gonalons \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma cho ph\u00e9p gia nh\u1eadp Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<h2>Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Claudio Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t Buffon gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain sau khi r\u1eddi Juventus. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Marchisio \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay th\u00e0nh Turin. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng &ldquo;Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed&rdquo; s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn MLS nh\u01b0ng PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi anh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Monaco theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd France Football \u0111\u01b0a tin Monaco \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida t\u1eeb Besiktas. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Croatia. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Monaco s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nGalatasaray nh\u1eafm sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AMK kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Galatasaray \u0111ang nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Emirates. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o tay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf Champions League. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Welbeck kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-178-cuu-sao-psg-khuyen-neymar-toi-real-184-194694.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8: C\u1ef1u sao PSG khuy\u00ean Neymar t\u1edbi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-178-barca-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-hau-ve-tiem-nang-184-194638.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8: Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5640","checkdouble":"194759"},{"date":"21:23 18/08","title":"Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Alaves d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n 2/3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, sau c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm. Th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Coutinho.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: BARCA 3-0 ALAVES\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/EifXOQ.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>Barca \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf  gi\u1ea3i International Champions Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t,  h\u1ecd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y  tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u00e0 Boca Juniors. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trong \u0111\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0  ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o  tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n La Liga 2018/19 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Nou Camp, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn  n\u00e0o \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc (th\u1eafng 16 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3 tr\u1eadn). Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa Andres Iniesta  \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t,  \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0  Arthur Melo, Malcom, Arturo Vidal.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t  ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 11 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169 t\u1eeb  m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Sergi Roberto xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf  h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Coutinho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng  xuy\u00ean \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta hay Rafinha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay  trong giao \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, ch\u1eb3ng r\u00f5 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i do \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng  2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN m\u00e0 Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh  Messi vs Suarez. Th\u1ef1c ra, v\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Alves ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n  d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 (thua 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Barca) th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c CLB x\u1ee9 Catalunya s\u1eed  d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra sao kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-Barca-vs-Alaves-bong-da-La-Liga-201819-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi, Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a Barca v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\nBarca chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1  Messi v\u1edbi c\u00fa volley n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Messi t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng  v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0 Jordi Alba di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa volley c\u0103ng  tr\u00fang v\u00e0o c\u1ea1nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1eeda hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u00f4i qua m\u00e0 Barcelona th\u1eadm ch\u00ed r\u1ea5t  hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf h\u00e0ng.\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t, chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp che ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n v\u00e0  c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i l\u0103n x\u1ea3 song c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y, Barca t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn,  k\u00e9m s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u do thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ivan Rakitic l\u00e0  ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a. Messi c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u  c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, Blaugrana m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00ean c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Alaves. Ph\u00fat 38, Messi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n  th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e0n em Dembele v\u00e0o th\u1ebf  \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pacheco nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p>Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Barca c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng  c\u00f4ng khi Coutinho th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Semedo. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Roberto s\u1ebd l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai  tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Coutinho \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, Barca \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1  kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, l\u00e0m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Alaves ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecdc h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho cung dong gop 1 ban cho Barca o tran nay sau khi vao san thay nguoi\" title=\"Coutinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n cho Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/4F32E5DC00000578-6074425-image-a-168_1534629881568.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Coutinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n cho Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc cho Barca  kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Lionel Messi. Ph\u00fat 64, El Pulga l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh  hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo ki\u1ec3u c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng t\u1ea7m cao m\u00e0  ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, s\u00e1t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o  ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean b\u1eaft b\u00e0i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alaves b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00ean  kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n b\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Messi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 sau v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp x\u1eed l\u00fd,  huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c cao c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Alaves nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o khung g\u1ed7 b\u1eadt ra. Ph\u00fat  73, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Luis Suarez t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng vui khi b\u1ecb Pacheco t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i pha d\u1ee9t  \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 83 th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.  Nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Arthur Melo, Coutinho d\u1eabn v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7  \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3i vung ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Pacheco. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng 2-0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft  qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Luis Suarez ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng  v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Alaves cho Messi kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf ch\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u00f3i quen r\u1ed3i tung ra  c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng cho Pacheco m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-Barca-vs-Alaves-bong-da-La-Liga-201819-hom-nay-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 3-0 Alaves</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng Barca r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\u00a0Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi La Liga th\u00ec xem ra, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi thi\u00ean t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBARCELONA (4-3-3): </strong>Marc-Andre ter Stegen; Nelson Semedo (Coutinho 46'), Gerard Pique, Samuel  Umtiti, Jordi Alba; Sergi Roberto, Sergio Busquets (Vidal 85'), Ivan Rakitic; Lionel Messi,  Luis Suarez, Ousmane Dembele (Arthur Melo 78')<br>\r\n<strong>ALAVES (4-1-4-1):</strong> Fernando Pacheco; Martin Aguirregabiria, Victor Laguardia,  Guillermo Maripan, Ruben Duarte; Daniel Torres (Adri\u00e1n Mar\u00edn 68'); Jony (Borja Bast\u00f3n 68'), Mubarak Wakaso, Manu  Garcia, Ibai Gomez; Ruben Sobrino (Burgui 71').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)</strong>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5639","checkdouble":"194762"},{"date":"04:06 19/08","title":"Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5638","checkdouble":"194775"},{"date":"04:20 19/08","title":"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00f2ng 26 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. Sau 22 n\u0103m n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Wenger, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh sang m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 HLV Emery. Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. Ti\u1ebfp ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecba Stamford Bridge c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Arsenal trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n khi Arsenal l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. <strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1992/93</strong>. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Arsenal m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn thua 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Norwich tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Blackburn \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGeorge Graham l\u00e0 HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1992/93 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw.</strong> Khi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n, Burtenshaw \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e1ng 3 \u2013 th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5637","checkdouble":"194776"},{"date":"04:30 19/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thu v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap Chelsea th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 v\u1edbi The Blues. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong 25 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t t\u1ea7m cao kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i c\u0169ng x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o thay Willian \u1edf ph\u00fat 60. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Alonso ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 25-30 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cao. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 90 ph\u00fat\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5636","checkdouble":"194777"}]}